<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 5% 10%;
            background-color: #ddd6fe;
            color: black;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.25rem;
        }

        .reset {
            background-color: #3b3b3b;
            ;
            width: 150px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 40px;
            color: #e7e7e7;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: 0.25s color;
        }

        .reset:hover {
            color: #fff;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <span>Dear <%= name %></span>
    <% if (isTeacherApproved) { %>
        <span>Congratulations, you are now a teacher on Renaissance.</span>
        <span>Proceed with creating course, lessons, quizzes and assignments. Enjoy!</span>
        <% } else { %>
            <span>We regret to inform you that your request for being a teacher in Renaissance has not been
                approved.</span>
            <span>Please contact the administrator for more information.</span>
            <% } %>
</body>

</html>